name: DNA Imprints
overview:
At DNA Imprints we celebrate your uniqueness by displaying you on canvas.

The study of biology dates back hundreds of years and mankindâ€™s yearning to create art dates back even further. As the study of biology and the creation of art developed into their own separate fields, we at DNA Imprints unite the two distinctive disciplines and provide you with the best personalized gift ever. Located in Southern California, a hotbed for science and art, DNA Imprints is at the forefront of combining these different branches of knowledge. We are a company made up of scientists and artists who one day, thought outside the lab and palette, to deliver the aesthetic value of fusing science and art right into your own living room.

DNA Imprints want to celebrate your life! Each person is born with their own unique DNA sequence and lead uniquely different lives. We at DNA Imprints have found a way to honor individuality to the highest degree. By utilizing the most personal possession you have in your body (your DNA), we have transformed it into innovative pieces of art that you, your family and friends can admire. We provide a variety of wall art and keepsakes for the celebration of your life, and of the imprints you have left on others. Please view our product lines and choose the ones you like.

DNA Imprints is sensitive to the values of life, family, and friends and want to help you capture the memories in the most unique and personal way. From your first child being born, your wedding day, or the celebration of a grandparentâ€™s 100th birthday, life never stops making imprints on your memories.
